msgstr "the blissful stilling of perception."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig1.6:4.3"
msgid "Ārādhayāhi nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "Win extinguishment,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig1.6:4.4"
